Author: SELFLLERY
Title: 🔥[ANN] SELFLLERY | TAKE PHOTO - MAKE MONEY 🔥
Body: YOU token transfer happens when users receive Likes (‘Proof-of-Like’). You can get money getting likes, so it motivates you to create a really cool visual content Or just to have a lot friends on the platform who like your photos anyway). At the moment 1 YOU = 0.001 ETH. The value of 1 YOU token may increase when the platform will become more popular. YOU tokens can be exchanged to ETH and then to cash or use in SELFLLERY. The purpose of SELFLLERY is to create an ecosystem that: 1. Enables users to monetize their photos, videos and live streams in a gamified way; 2. Supports charitable organizations and makes donations easy for users; 3. Provides companies with easy-to-use and effective promotion tools that involve user photos; 4. Expands the market of photo and video content for companies and news services, with a convenient search functionality; 5. Integrates modern technologies and capabilities of blockchain into the digital photography market, increasing the transparency and security of its transactions.

Author: SELFLLERY
Title: 🔥[ANN] SELFLLERY | TAKE PHOTO - MAKE MONEY 🔥
Body: SELFLLERY at Blockchain Middle East Forum in Dubai  The first step before a giant leap - our first conference after pre-TGE. As we promised we keep you informed about our road show. Now we're in Dubai, at Blockchain Middle East Forum. The conference took place from 5 to 6 of February and it was a successful one, from our point of view. Check it out at blockchainme.iqpc.ae. Why Dubai? Because it wants to become the first blockchain-powered government in the world by 2020. And it has all the chances, as we see it. Being the part of United Arab Emirates, it has the dependence on oil, that's why it develops the technologies, with the goal of becoming one of the biggest global business hubs, reducing the dependence. This goal attracts many public and private startups, and provides all the necessary conditions for domestic [Suspicious link removed]panies. Among speakers we saw many Dubai authorities, like Haroun Dharsey, Senior Vice President of Dubai Islamic Bank, Sultan Al Akraf, Head of Real Estate Registration of Dubai Land Department and Waleed Aldhuhouri, Head of Corporate Applications of Dubai Health Authority. But it's wasn't all about Dubai government, it was also about wonderful technologies. So we had a pleasure to hear about such companies as Bankex, Innoopolis, Altair, Bitcar and Shelterzoom. At conference, we met many colleagues, made some connections, saw many innovative startups and, of course, demonstrated our SELFLLERY platform to attendees and visitors. We're seeing some unstoppable interest to our product wherever we go. It has a real use application, and that's why our users base is growing constantly. Next stop? We'll keep posting the updates, so stay tuned! You can find photos from this event on our facebook https://www.facebook.com/Selfllery/

SELF want to solve the Problem of Visual Content Monetization and allows normal users to monetize their photos by default. On Traditional websites, photo content monetization are present only in two forms: either by placing advertisements on web pages with photos or via direct sale of the photographs. Both scenarios assume the commercial use of the photograph. Therefore, the requirements for such content are high, which creates barriers for the authors. On SELF would much easy, so everybody will be able to monetize their content, you don't need to be artist.

Author: SocialCloud
Title: 🔥[ANN] SELFLLERY | TAKE PHOTO - MAKE MONEY 🔥
Body: WEBSITE | WHITEPAPER | TWITTER | FACEBOOK | TELEGRAM | MEDIUM | REDDIT  JOIN OUR TELEGRAM CHAT https://t.me/selfllery_en    Selfllery is a multifunctional social platform that allows you to receive rewards in cryptocurrency  for social activities related to publication and distribution of visual content. The product concept and its first versions were designed in early 2016. The Selfllery reward system is based on blockchain technology.    Selfllery enables people to make their visual content truly rewarding. The purpose of Selfllery is to create an ecosystem that: 1. Enables users to monetize their photos, videos and live streams in a gamified way; 2. Supports charitable organizations and makes donations easy for users; 3. Provides companies with easy-to-use and effective promotion tools that involve user photos; 4. Expands the market of photo and video content for companies and news services, with a convenient search functionality; 5. Integrates modern technologies and capabilities of blockchain into the digital photography market, increasing the transparency and security of its transactions.    Initially, YOU tokens are generated during the TGE based on the Ethereum platform. Buyers receive YOU in exchange for Ethereum (ETH) tokens by sending a payment to a smart contract that generates YOU tokens. The smart contract address will be published on official Selfllery website one day before the TGE start.  YOU token price: 1 YOU = 0.001 ETH The minimum goal (soft cap): 10 000 ETH The maximum goal (hard cap): 55 000 ETH Minimum purchase amount: 0.1 ETH  TGE will have two stages: pre-sale and main sale. At the pre-sale stage, YOU tokens are offered only to whitelisted buyers, whereas during the main sale tokens can be purchased by anyone. During pre-sale, early buyers can buy YOU tokens at a discount. For discounted YOU tokens, the minimum purchase amount is set at 10 ETH and tokens are locked up for at least one month after the main sale ends.    The Selfllery platform combines: - YOU Token - Monetizing Visual Content - Monetization of Social Activities - Stock Photo - Marketing platform - Charity platform - Photo-Quests and Photo-Contests    Initial Distribution of YOU Tokens generated during TGE: - YOU Token - Monetizing Visual Content - Monetization of Social Activities - Stock Photo - Marketing platform - Charity platform - Photo-Quests and Photo-Contests    Q1 2016 Idea, domain research Product concept definition  Q2 2016 Alpha version of Web interface Alpha version of Android application  Q3 2016 Inside testing of the WEB interface Inside testing of the Android application  Q4 2016 Beta version of Android application User testing of the service  Q1 2017 Market research and analysis White Paper preparation  Q2 2017 Economic model validation Advisor consulting  Q3 2017 Pre-launch of TGE  Q4 2017 Pre-TGE campaign launch Pre-TGE launch Photo contest module Charity module Expansion of the team for TGE  Q1 2018 TGE Launch Team expansion Marketplace Advertising module Photo editing filters Beta version of iOS application  Q2 2018 >FUTURE Additional modules development Global marketing campaign  Indonesian https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2775143 Thanks to portgas313 Turkish https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2779283 Thanks to hbcenk Chinese https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2784596 Thanks to kkndkill Hindi https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2829920 Thanks to imtiazmahmood Japanese https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2841396 Thanks to imtiazmahmood Spanish https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2768446 Thanks to EdChain
